GSD.product_version: versions from v5.15 to before v6.0.13
GSD.description:
octeontx2-pf: Fix potential memory leak in otx2_init_tc()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.13 by commit db5ec358cf4ef0ab382ee733d05f018e8bef9462, it was introduced in version v5.15 by commit 2e2a8126ffac66b9b177ce78ad430281c0c8cc74. For more details please see the references link.
